76561198042109902,Recommended,276770,20168575,"Posted: 31 December, 2015",all,G4MB1T,"A TD game where you take control of hero units or the towers you build.A game throwback to several playable franchises like he-man and gi.joe.Simple you build towers, upgrade towers take contro lof towers and destroy the enemy.It is quite shortlived as a game and only worth i would say on a sale and as a casual game. Once you figure out which army you like and what and how their towers work can easily take down any wave of enemies. I kept choosing and having a certain play style with Cobra and found that was getting quite easy with my stragety so after playing it few times after beating the game i lost interest, BUT i still had fun with it and if I used it as a casual game rather than pump few hours into it straight away it may have been more long lived."
